Name: Average time from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time for all instances of 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Time from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' for manuscripts that undergo major revision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' in the process of manuscript submission to acceptance or rejection
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' from the start of the submission process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'

Name: Total time it takes 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' after 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'

Name: Minimum time for 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission and the end of the case

Name: Average time to 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' after 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time of 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' cycle from submission to decision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average time for 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' in manuscripts that were accepted without major revisions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Total time from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' in the review process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' in cases leading to immediate reject decisions
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'
